were - you see, you get ten and thirteen years - the younger three, you see, mother had we three girls I was the second of the first three then there were two boys and then another three girls you see that there was ten to - ten, twelve, thirteen years wh
ich is a lot. My youngest sister, I suppose she\rquote d be about four years old when I was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14708622 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16204869\charrsid8939483 .
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5390660 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16204869\charrsid8939483 Not really old enough to do anything for you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10690358 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16204869\charrsid8939483 No. No, as a matter of fact I think }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3692618\charrsid8939483 when}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid16204869\charrsid8939483  we were home we rather spoilt the - the younger three, we did so much for them. But out of the - now my eldest sister she hadn\rquote t a clue, she\rquote d - to - furnish a home, she\rquote s always in a muddle. She
\rquote s wasteful with - with cooking and food. Wasteful altogether. She\rquote s a bad - always has been, bad housekeeper. And the youngest sister, she is very artistic, very clever, very lovely home. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid3692618\charrsid8939483 But the other two from her, no, they - they\rquote re all right but - they\rquote re not the least bit artistic. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16204869\charrsid8939483 And they\rquote 
