\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5390660 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3692618\charrsid8939483 What sort of people do you think you\rquote re parents hoped you\rquote d grow up to be, do you remember
