\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3692618\charrsid8939483 , mother\rquote s advice was to look after the inner man, the food, food and warmth, and t
he comfort in the home. Comfortable, warm home and good food, that was the main the To look after the inner man, she said, look after your husband\rquote s food and - and - and comfortable fires and - and nice home. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
