n used. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16204869\charrsid8939483 Very strict on that. And very strict on us - going - going to }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3692618\charrsid8939483 church,}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
