}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3692618\charrsid8939483  way I see you only - you stir them up to do more, if you go out and say, oh, you know, you shouldn\rquote t do that really, you know, go in a nice}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
