 you know to keep our hats on. And the elastic had broken off my - hat. My mother was sewing this elastic on. That girl went and told everybody my mother was wicked because she was sewing that elast
ic on my hat. Now that was wicked. And I had all this, all these girls saying you\rquote ve got a wicked mother, sews on Sunday. And I think that - that was the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9192541\charrsid8939483 beginning}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
