\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10690358 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16204869\charrsid8939483 Yes. And I said, I shall never forget, every time I hear it I go back. And I said to him, another thing very }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
