\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5390660 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16204869\charrsid8939483 Were there any gangs or }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15809763\charrsid8939483 cliques}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
