\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9192541\charrsid8939483 cliquey}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16204869\charrsid8939483  or anything like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5390660 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16204869\charrsid8939483 Do you remember any children who were left out of things, who seemed to be on their own more than the others?
