\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10690358 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16204869\charrsid8939483 Well probably had some }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15809763\charrsid8939483 meanness}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid16204869\charrsid8939483  about them, now - you\rquote d get some, for instance, that the - I remember 
- one girl, she used to pick our names to pieces and call us Ashes and our name was Ashley, we used to be called Ashes - Ashes in the grate or something of that and - and - another girl, her name was, well she was a friend of mine, Napman. They used to ca
