\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5390660 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16204869\charrsid8939483 There weren\rquote t any children who came from }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9192541\charrsid8939483 really}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
