t know, we never -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5390660 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16204869\charrsid8939483 You don\rquote t know really what the reasons were?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10690358 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16204869\charrsid8939483 No. Never knew why but there were - there were favourites definitely.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5390660 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16204869\charrsid8939483 Do you ever remember your mother meeting the teachers, apart from that incident when she went up to the school, did she ever visit t
he school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10690358 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16204869\charrsid8939483 No, only - only if she went to school }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15809763\charrsid8939483 or}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
