\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16204869\charrsid8939483  when I was - a - a teenager. I had - my mother\rquote 
s sister at Peterborough and she had ten children, my grandmother would - no, my grandmother died when I was seventeen, we - but - we used to go to Peterborough and used to go to Yaxley to my grandmother\rquote 
s - for holidays. After we once set off, you know, left school and - and had these jobs, we never went with our parents. We went our - oh I was about sixteen I think when I went first of all on my own for a holiday, yes I w
ould - would have been that. And I went to Peterborough. And I - I can remember that, thinking oh lovely - the first holiday really go - on your own.
