I was only just - we two and he used to - I think I used to get his breakfast in the morning. And very seldom he was home to a meal at night. She was a very sad woman.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5390660 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16204869\charrsid8939483 Did she get up for breakfast at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10690358 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16204869\charrsid8939483 Yes, she used to get up for breakfast.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5390660 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16204869\charrsid8939483 How often in a week would you }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13108354\charrsid8939483 have meat}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
