\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5390660 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16204869\charrsid8939483 Nothing like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10690358 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16204869\charrsid8939483 No. Oh it\rquote d be boiled - boiled egg or piece of fish midday - and perhaps you\rquote ll be lucky if you had a piece of }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13108354\charrsid8939483 cheese}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16204869\charrsid8939483  at 
