m going down to the shops - it was more or less going for a drink. Now sometimes - she\rquote d have the drink and then she\rquote d say, oh we\rquote ll go out 
for a - for a drive. She'd hire a car, he'd - that'd go down to his account - we'll go out for a drive. For a drive out }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13108354\charrsid8939483 somewhere}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
