We used to get - half a pig's head or sheep's head, something of that, I\rquote ve forgotten now, it\rquote s so many years ago that - and so much beef, shin of; beef I think it was and we used to cook the two together and - and then they\rquote 
d all come to jelly and then when it was cold you\rquote d pick all that meat off all the bone, and then warm up the jelly, seasoning and all that with it and then you\rquote 
d - you put it in a deep basin and put all this gravy over and it used to set into a lovely jelly and you would cut that and have - probably high tea and that and just salad things like that or have it for supper.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
